00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:07,730
Do you recognize this drawing?

283
00:19:16,790 --> 00:19:17,980
It belongs to my father.

284
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:19,380
I've seen it since young.

285
00:19:19,510 --> 00:19:20,220
Of course, I recognize it.

286
00:19:21,350 --> 00:19:22,810
This is it.

287
00:19:23,270 --> 00:19:24,530
Why do you have this painting?

288
00:19:25,030 --> 00:19:26,730
This painting was in Shi Yiping's residence.

289
00:19:27,070 --> 00:19:29,420
Zang Hai requested it from the Emperor after his death.

290
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:31,250
Why would Shi Yiping

291
00:19:31,590 --> 00:19:33,380
possess my father's painting?

292
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:36,810
Whatever.

293
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:40,050
Zang Hai is such a sweet person.

294
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:41,690
He requested

295
00:19:41,690 --> 00:19:43,330
a painting of Dongxia from the Emperor for you

296
00:19:43,790 --> 00:19:44,940
so you won't feel homesick.

297
00:19:45,830 --> 00:19:46,420
That's right.

298
00:19:46,680 --> 00:19:47,770
He has no time to accompany me.

299
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:49,010
He owes me this painting.

300
00:19:53,830 --> 00:19:54,620
All right.

301
00:19:54,750 --> 00:19:56,220
You shouldn't stay in your house all the time.

302
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:57,460
Come and have fun with me outside.

303
00:20:06,110 --> 00:20:06,700
Mr. Zhao,

304
00:20:08,240 --> 00:20:11,140
I have something I don't understand. Please guide me.

305
00:20:14,510 --> 00:20:17,050
The documents submitted by the Ministry of Works recently

306
00:20:17,550 --> 00:20:20,090
were all rejected by the Cabinet.

307
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,180
It's spring

308
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:23,810
and many places suffer from floods.

309
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:25,700
The Ministry of Works knows the damage it will cause

310
00:20:26,160 --> 00:20:27,220
and wants to improve the flood control system

311
00:20:27,590 --> 00:20:28,610
but for some reason...

312
00:20:28,610 --> 00:20:29,600
Zang Hai.

313
00:20:32,070 --> 00:20:33,010
In recent years,

314
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:35,570
Yong's treasury has been drained.

315
00:20:36,640 --> 00:20:37,810
Even the Ministry of Rites

316
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:41,660
struggled to organize the Spring Exam, let alone the Ministry of Works.

317
00:20:42,510 --> 00:20:47,330
If we keep allocating money to every ministry's needs,

318
00:20:48,510 --> 00:20:50,050
we're going to create a bigger problem.

319
00:20:52,270 --> 00:20:55,700
This problem must be dealt with from its roots.

320
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:59,490
Are you talking about getting rid of corruption?

321
00:20:59,590 --> 00:21:00,010
That's right.

322
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:01,980
The treasury's money

323
00:21:03,030 --> 00:21:05,290
has gone to the corrupt officials.

324
00:21:06,310 --> 00:21:07,620
It's no use no matter how much money you allocate.

325
00:21:08,310 --> 00:21:11,490
In the end, it's the problem of the law.

326
00:21:12,510 --> 00:21:13,290
A heavy punishment is needed

327
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:16,140
to get rid of corruption.

328
00:21:19,790 --> 00:21:20,660
But doing this

329
00:21:21,590 --> 00:21:22,810
will bring the opposite effect.

330
00:21:25,640 --> 00:21:27,220
Zang Hai.

331
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:33,010
If you can think of that,

332
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:39,090
it's very good.

333
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:42,940
This is also what I'm most worried about.

334
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:45,380
The corruption culture in the imperial court

335
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:47,810
happens mostly due to officials

336
00:21:48,400 --> 00:21:50,860
who can't feed their families with their meager salaries.

337
00:21:52,270 --> 00:21:55,810
If you don't want them to harm the common people,

338
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:58,530
killing a few of them won't solve the problem.

339
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:02,660
I've petitioned the Emperor

340
00:22:03,790 --> 00:22:05,900
to increase the salaries of all fifth-rank officials and above

341
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:07,570
by 30%.

342
00:22:12,110 --> 00:22:13,140
This is the money

343
00:22:14,110 --> 00:22:17,530
that the imperial court must spend.

344
00:22:18,960 --> 00:22:20,090
One must have a roof above their head

345
00:22:20,270 --> 00:22:21,530
and a full tummy.

346
00:22:22,350 --> 00:22:23,900
Officials must be able to feed their families

347
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:25,530
so they don't prey on the people.

348
00:22:27,030 --> 00:22:28,490
This is a good method indeed.

349
00:22:30,350 --> 00:22:30,940
However...

350
00:22:32,070 --> 00:22:33,140
shouldn't we start

351
00:22:33,140 --> 00:22:34,730
from those working closely with the people?

352
00:22:35,400 --> 00:22:37,770
If the treasury has a lot of money,

353
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:39,810
I will surely do that.

354
00:22:40,720 --> 00:22:43,380
However, prioritizing the small officials

355
00:22:44,110 --> 00:22:46,090
over the powerful officials

356
00:22:48,550 --> 00:22:50,810
is not something even the Emperor can do.

357
00:22:56,030 --> 00:22:59,220
As the saying goes, "If one intends to take something,

358
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:01,770
one must first give something away."

359
00:23:05,830 --> 00:23:07,380
You are involved in the imperial court now.

360
00:23:08,070 --> 00:23:11,330
You must remember this in the future.

361
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:12,980
Yes.

362
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:14,490
I will remember it.

363
00:23:21,350 --> 00:23:22,420
Tong'er came today

364
00:23:22,790 --> 00:23:24,660
and recognized the painting to be Mr. Zhao's.

365
00:23:24,960 --> 00:23:26,380
She even asked why the painting ended up in our place.

366
00:23:31,550 --> 00:23:32,530
It's his indeed.

367
00:23:33,070 --> 00:23:35,660
This is very suspicious indeed.

368
00:23:40,550 --> 00:23:42,420
I've never lied to Tong'er before.

369
00:23:43,000 --> 00:23:44,330
I didn't tell her the truth today

370
00:23:45,070 --> 00:23:46,380
and I feel a little guilty.

371
00:23:46,830 --> 00:23:48,090
She is my best friend.

372
00:23:49,680 --> 00:23:52,010
I really hope Mr. Zhao is just your benefactor

373
00:23:52,510 --> 00:23:53,530
and not your enemy.

374
00:24:13,350 --> 00:24:13,980
Tong'er.

375
00:24:15,790 --> 00:24:16,290
Father.

376
00:24:18,590 --> 00:24:19,490
What are you looking for?

377
00:24:20,830 --> 00:24:21,380
Father.

378
00:24:21,750 --> 00:24:24,490
Did you give Shi Yiping this painting?

379
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:27,490
Which painting?

380
00:24:28,550 --> 00:24:29,860
The "Landscape of Mount Yuren" painting

381
00:24:30,590 --> 00:24:31,810
that was kept here previously.

382
00:24:33,510 --> 00:24:34,370
That painting?

383
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:37,420
Previously,

384
00:24:37,790 --> 00:24:40,460
I went to visit the Shi residence

385
00:24:40,830 --> 00:24:42,050
with my colleagues

386
00:24:42,240 --> 00:24:44,810
for a so-called painting and calligraphy appreciation session.

387
00:24:46,200 --> 00:24:48,420
I brought this painting with me without much thought.

388
00:24:49,240 --> 00:24:51,490
To my surprise, he loved it.

389
00:24:51,960 --> 00:24:53,010
He forced me to give it to him

390
00:24:53,310 --> 00:24:54,330
so I did.

391
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:56,860
I went to hang out with Antu today

392
00:24:57,510 --> 00:24:59,140
and saw this painting at her place.

393
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:01,090
I thought I was mistaken

394
00:25:01,750 --> 00:25:02,980
but when I came back and looked for it,

395
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:04,330
the painting was indeed yours.

396
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:09,220
This painting should belong to the imperial court

397
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:11,090
now that Shi Residence was seized

398
00:25:12,590 --> 00:25:14,490
following Shi Yiping's death.

399
00:25:16,030 --> 00:25:17,250
How come she possesses the painting?

400
00:25:19,960 --> 00:25:20,700
She said

401
00:25:21,200 --> 00:25:23,660
Zang Hai purposely asked the Emperor for it

402
00:25:24,070 --> 00:25:25,530
to be given to her as a gift

403
00:25:25,760 --> 00:25:26,900
because it was a painting of Dongxia.

404
00:25:30,110 --> 00:25:31,140
I see.

405
00:25:33,240 --> 00:25:33,770
Tong'er.

406
00:25:35,550 --> 00:25:36,490
Sit with me for a while.

407
00:25:45,550 --> 00:25:47,380
Since your mother passed away,

408
00:25:49,160 --> 00:25:52,140
both of us have been relying on each other

409
00:25:52,640 --> 00:25:54,050
so I allowed you

410
00:25:56,000 --> 00:25:58,980
to go to Zhen Tower as a man

411
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:01,250
to tell stories.

412
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:03,290
Right now,

413
00:26:05,510 --> 00:26:06,730
you are no longer a child.

414
00:26:08,270 --> 00:26:09,810
It's time to act your age.

415
00:26:10,350 --> 00:26:11,250
But I enjoy

416
00:26:11,270 --> 00:26:12,980
reading and telling stories.

417
00:26:15,790 --> 00:26:16,860
You've been rebellious

418
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:19,860
since your childhood

419
00:26:20,350 --> 00:26:21,660
because I've always doted on you.

420
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:25,050
You do things without caring about the consequences.

421
00:26:25,350 --> 00:26:27,010
You will regret it one day.

422
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:28,420
Father.

423
00:26:29,510 --> 00:26:30,940
Zhen Tower is gone now.

424
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:34,420
You should cease thinking about telling and reading stories anymore.

425
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:35,770
From now on,

426
00:26:36,200 --> 00:26:38,980
you should stay home and accompany me more.

427
00:26:42,550 --> 00:26:43,090
Master.

428
00:26:47,070 --> 00:26:48,090
I'm going to work.

429
00:26:49,510 --> 00:26:50,570
Go back and rest.

430
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:14,570
Zhao Geng.

431
00:27:15,510 --> 00:27:16,140
Yes, Master.

432
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:18,290
Tong'er is a lady now.

433
00:27:21,550 --> 00:27:22,730
When she goes out in the future,

434
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:25,570
assign a few men to follow her

435
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:27,940
in case anything happens to her.

436
00:27:28,350 --> 00:27:28,810
Yes.

437
00:27:47,590 --> 00:27:50,140
Mr. Zang, it's late.

438
00:27:51,110 --> 00:27:52,420
Our work is endless.

439
00:27:52,510 --> 00:27:53,620
Continue tomorrow.

440
00:27:54,130 --> 00:27:56,250
I still have work to do from the Ministry of Works

441
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:57,180
and Imperial Astronomical Bureau tomorrow.

442
00:27:58,000 --> 00:28:00,140
Mr. Shi used to reprimand me in the past

443
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:02,180
for being lazy and carefree.

444
00:28:02,790 --> 00:28:04,250
If he sees you now,

445
00:28:04,510 --> 00:28:06,250
he will surely appreciate you.

446
00:28:08,110 --> 00:28:09,050
I'll be going back.

447
00:28:15,510 --> 00:28:16,290
What a pity.

448
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:18,050
I joined the Cabinet too late.

449
00:28:18,510 --> 00:28:20,770
Otherwise, I could learn from Mr. Shi.

450
00:28:21,550 --> 00:28:22,620
Having a superior

451
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:24,010
who keeps giving me reminders

452
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:26,090
in political affairs

453
00:28:26,590 --> 00:28:27,330
is a lucky thing.

454
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:29,900
You are different

455
00:28:30,350 --> 00:28:31,490
from what I imagined.

456
00:28:34,830 --> 00:28:35,770
What do you mean?

457
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:38,490
Mr. Zang,

458
00:28:38,830 --> 00:28:41,380
you served Zhuang Luyin in the past.

459
00:28:42,350 --> 00:28:43,980
You became an official through recommendation.

460
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:48,090
However, you caused a mess in the imperial court.

461
00:28:48,550 --> 00:28:50,140
In Mr. Shi's opinion,

462
00:28:50,480 --> 00:28:51,460
you broke

463
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:53,940
the balance he spent his whole life maintaining.

464
00:28:54,510 --> 00:28:55,010
Balance?

465
00:28:56,790 --> 00:28:57,620
But didn't Mr. Shi

466
00:28:58,160 --> 00:29:00,330
turn a blind eye

467
00:29:00,830 --> 00:29:01,900
on what Cao Jingxian did?

468
00:29:03,070 --> 00:29:05,420
Cao Jingxian and Zhuang Luyin

469
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:08,900
were two authoritative figures no one would dare offend.

470
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:10,730
Mr. Shi has been going against them

471
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:12,330
by leading the Cabinet.

472
00:29:12,640 --> 00:29:14,180
Both of them are dead now.

473
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:17,980
Unfortunately, Mr. Shi passed away as well.

474
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:21,810
However, rumors in the capital are saying

475
00:29:22,270 --> 00:29:25,050
that Mr. Shi was close to Cao Jingxian.

476
00:29:26,070 --> 00:29:27,180
However, he was killed

477
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:29,900
by Cao Jingxian's surveillance officers.

478
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:33,290
They say both of them had a falling out

479
00:29:33,640 --> 00:29:34,570
and turned against each other.

480
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:35,290
Impossible.

481
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:36,330
I don't believe it.

482
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:38,660
Mr. Shi was my superior for many years.

483
00:29:39,070 --> 00:29:39,860
I know him

484
00:29:39,860 --> 00:29:40,730
very well.

485
00:29:41,350 --> 00:29:41,980
Mr. Zang,

486
00:29:42,350 --> 00:29:43,330
let me show you something.

487
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:54,620
This is the name list of Yong's officials.

488
00:29:54,790 --> 00:29:56,220
Mr. Shi gave it to me back then.

489
00:29:56,790 --> 00:29:58,230
He started writing this name list

490
00:29:58,240 --> 00:29:59,770
when he was the Vice Minister of Personnel.

491
00:30:04,030 --> 00:30:05,290
Everyone said Mr. Shi

492
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:07,050
remembered every official of Yong

493
00:30:07,270 --> 00:30:09,220
when he was the Vice Minister of Personnel.

494
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:12,570
I suppose good memory still has to make way

495
00:30:12,750 --> 00:30:13,700
for note-taking.

496
00:30:14,590 --> 00:30:15,460
Before the New Year,

497
00:30:15,720 --> 00:30:17,140
Mr. Shi saw I was busy working

498
00:30:17,140 --> 00:30:18,070
[Zhuang Luyin, the 19th Year of Zhenshun era, Dead]

499
00:30:18,070 --> 00:30:19,570
and gave me this name list.

500
00:30:20,240 --> 00:30:22,620
The name list has always been kept at the Cabinet

501
00:30:22,960 --> 00:30:24,010
with no one to retrieve it.

502
00:30:26,020 --> 00:30:29,100
[Cao Jingxian, Lu Min]

503
00:30:30,510 --> 00:30:31,290
Lu Min?

504
00:30:31,700 --> 00:30:34,060
[Cao Jingxian, Lu Min]

505
00:30:37,350 --> 00:30:38,330
Lu Min...

506
00:30:39,790 --> 00:30:41,090
I noticed this before.

507
00:30:42,000 --> 00:30:44,250
This should be Cao Jingxian's name before he entered the palace.

508
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:46,940
All his foster sons have the Lu surname.

509
00:30:48,400 --> 00:30:50,860
He just couldn't give up on passing his lineage.

510
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:09,140
Sir.

511
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:13,140
I didn't know you were coming.

512
00:31:13,750 --> 00:31:15,570
Sorry for the poor reception.

513
00:31:16,790 --> 00:31:17,250
Sit.

514
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:19,620
Thank you, sir.

515
00:31:21,270 --> 00:31:22,010
You may leave.

516
00:31:30,510 --> 00:31:31,530
Are you the eunuch, Mr. Liu?

517
00:31:32,310 --> 00:31:33,660
Yes.

518
00:31:35,590 --> 00:31:37,980
You were the one who taught the new eunuchs

519
00:31:38,830 --> 00:31:40,090
the rules in the past.

520
00:31:41,350 --> 00:31:42,420
I want to ask you about someone.

521
00:31:42,830 --> 00:31:43,940
If I know something,

522
00:31:44,790 --> 00:31:46,620
I will tell you honestly.

523
00:31:47,880 --> 00:31:48,620
Lu Min.

524
00:31:49,750 --> 00:31:50,490
Lu Min?

525
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:53,660
Lu Min...

526
00:31:56,750 --> 00:31:57,490
I remember.

527
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,220
Do you still remember?

528
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:01,180
I do.

529
00:32:01,680 --> 00:32:02,880
He wasn't castrated

530
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:06,140
when he entered the palace.

531
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:08,460
He never had manhood

532
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:11,530
to begin with.

533
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:14,380
He castrated himself.

534
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:27,290
There are many rules and forms of etiquette in the palace.

535
00:32:28,070 --> 00:32:30,220
Those who graduated here

536
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:34,380
can have a chance of becoming a eunuch at the inner palace.

537
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:37,530
Lu Min was hardworking

538
00:32:37,790 --> 00:32:39,120
and liked to study.

539
00:32:39,720 --> 00:32:40,940
It didn't take long for him

540
00:32:41,480 --> 00:32:44,460
to learn most of the skills

541
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:47,770
from veterans like us.

542
00:32:49,270 --> 00:32:51,530
When it was time for him

543
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:53,490
to change his name and enter the palace,

544
00:32:54,160 --> 00:32:54,730
he was

545
00:32:55,270 --> 00:32:58,530
more capable than the eunuch,

546
00:32:58,960 --> 00:33:00,620
several years his senior.

547
00:33:01,480 --> 00:33:03,220
What did he change his name into later?

548
00:33:04,640 --> 00:33:07,010
I don't remember.

549
00:33:07,680 --> 00:33:08,770
I remember

550
00:33:09,070 --> 00:33:14,010
he went to work at the Imperial Stables Directorate.

551
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:16,730
Lu Min was educated

552
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:18,180
and he could read.

553
00:33:18,350 --> 00:33:21,140
He spoke in a formal and elegant way.

554
00:33:21,790 --> 00:33:22,770
He used to say

555
00:33:23,270 --> 00:33:24,940
that he shouldn't become a eunuch.

556
00:33:25,510 --> 00:33:27,140
He said if he participated in an exam,

557
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:29,140
he would surely become a highly-ranked official.

558
00:33:29,640 --> 00:33:30,980
He told me

559
00:33:31,350 --> 00:33:34,620
he used to study in the best academy in the capital.

560
00:33:35,440 --> 00:33:38,250
He studied at the Academy of Yong.

561
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:50,490
Sir.

562
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:53,900
All the original documents and files

563
00:33:54,110 --> 00:33:56,140
since the establishment of the Academy of Yong

564
00:33:56,270 --> 00:33:57,900
are stored here.

565
00:33:59,270 --> 00:34:00,010
You may leave.

566
00:34:00,440 --> 00:34:01,420
I can search for it myself.

567
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:02,380
Yes.

