00:35:42,460 --> 00:35:47,900
[Zhao Bingwen]

574
00:36:17,230 --> 00:36:17,940
Master.

575
00:36:19,190 --> 00:36:19,900
You're back?

576
00:36:20,590 --> 00:36:21,570
We are having Fried Bean Sauce Noodles tonight.

577
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:22,690
Wait for a while.

578
00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:25,690
I'm too tired today

579
00:36:26,110 --> 00:36:26,900
and don't have an appetite.

580
00:36:27,190 --> 00:36:28,130
I want to rest for a while.

581
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:29,780
The Cabinet

582
00:36:30,230 --> 00:36:31,900
is a difficult place to be.

583
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,130
Seriously.

584
00:36:33,670 --> 00:36:34,820
You hold three positions at once.

585
00:36:35,150 --> 00:36:36,570
There are too many things you need to do.

586
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:38,170
I feel exhausted for you already.

587
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:40,570
All of these responsibilities

588
00:36:41,110 --> 00:36:42,170
are too many

589
00:36:43,070 --> 00:36:43,940
and too heavy for me.

590
00:36:46,110 --> 00:36:49,050
Why don't I tell Bingwen

591
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:52,170
and ask him to relieve you of your burden?

592
00:36:52,480 --> 00:36:53,380
I'll think about it.

593
00:36:54,110 --> 00:36:55,130
Once I think it through,

594
00:36:55,670 --> 00:36:56,530
I'll tell him myself.

595
00:36:57,710 --> 00:36:58,340
Hai.

596
00:37:02,710 --> 00:37:04,690
You're like a stranger to me now.

597
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:07,780
You won't even chat with me.

598
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:10,570
Have you forgotten about me

599
00:37:10,630 --> 00:37:11,610
after you have Miss Xiang?

600
00:37:14,710 --> 00:37:16,170
When you put it like that,

601
00:37:16,960 --> 00:37:17,690
I have no choice

602
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:19,780
but to chat with you.

603
00:37:21,630 --> 00:37:22,570
That's more like it.

604
00:37:24,150 --> 00:37:24,690
Peel the garlic.

605
00:37:28,710 --> 00:37:29,260
Master,

606
00:37:30,070 --> 00:37:32,050
do you still remember when you asked me

607
00:37:32,670 --> 00:37:33,900
what kind of life I would want to live

608
00:37:34,230 --> 00:37:35,530
after getting my revenge?

609
00:37:38,110 --> 00:37:39,260
I couldn't answer you back then.

610
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:41,690
You also told me

611
00:37:42,480 --> 00:37:43,940
the day would come soon.

612
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:48,380
You were right.

613
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:52,300
I've made my choice

614
00:37:53,710 --> 00:37:56,610
and I'm still an official with my benefactor.

615
00:37:59,000 --> 00:37:59,940
But I want to know

616
00:38:00,710 --> 00:38:01,610
your answer.

617
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:03,650
Me?

618
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:07,900
My benefactor asked you

619
00:38:08,230 --> 00:38:09,090
to aid me in my revenge.

620
00:38:10,030 --> 00:38:11,170
Now that I've taken my revenge,

621
00:38:11,670 --> 00:38:13,170
haven't you thought about

622
00:38:13,590 --> 00:38:14,900
what you want to do?

623
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:28,610
Are you calling me useless now?

624
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,610
Since you're in the Cabinet now,

625
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:33,690
you no longer need the things I taught you.

626
00:38:34,150 --> 00:38:35,260
That's not what I mean.

627
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:38,210
I know that's not what you meant.

628
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:40,260
I was just teasing you.

629
00:38:45,400 --> 00:38:46,090
Do you really want to know?

630
00:38:59,510 --> 00:39:00,740
Royal silver.

631
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:04,260
Master,

632
00:39:04,510 --> 00:39:07,090
do you still remember the time when you took me

633
00:39:07,190 --> 00:39:08,690
to trick a corrupt official when I was young?

634
00:39:09,280 --> 00:39:10,260
I remember.

635
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:11,740
Look.

636
00:39:12,510 --> 00:39:13,260
I have

637
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:16,380
gotten the newly minted royal silver now.

638
00:39:19,670 --> 00:39:21,380
Look how much you've achieved.

639
00:39:22,070 --> 00:39:23,610
The royal silver I used back then

640
00:39:23,670 --> 00:39:25,380
was the tuition fee I received from your benefactor.

641
00:39:26,360 --> 00:39:26,980
Yet,

642
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:28,740
I spent all of it in the first lesson.

643
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:34,460
You are good at pretending to be an official.

644
00:39:35,070 --> 00:39:37,650
Did you learn it from my benefactor?

645
00:39:38,670 --> 00:39:40,690
Why don't you become an official?

646
00:39:42,030 --> 00:39:42,980
That won't do.

647
00:39:44,480 --> 00:39:46,260
I'm just a fraud.

648
00:39:46,510 --> 00:39:48,340
I'll be exposed if I become an official.

649
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:54,260
I don't think so.

650
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:01,940
As a person,

651
00:40:02,960 --> 00:40:04,170
we don't need to live

652
00:40:04,230 --> 00:40:06,210
for a certain goal.

653
00:40:06,710 --> 00:40:08,170
Living our days

654
00:40:08,630 --> 00:40:10,170
with people we care about by our side,

655
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:11,340
doesn't it sound good?

656
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:12,940
You are in the capital

657
00:40:13,230 --> 00:40:14,530
and your benefactor is also in the capital.

658
00:40:15,190 --> 00:40:16,530
Where else can I go?

659
00:40:17,230 --> 00:40:19,050
I'll just serve you

660
00:40:19,760 --> 00:40:20,570
and become a cook.

661
00:40:21,550 --> 00:40:23,530
If I can't teach you anything else,

662
00:40:23,880 --> 00:40:25,690
I'll feed you instead.

663
00:40:35,070 --> 00:40:36,460
You used to tell me

664
00:40:37,670 --> 00:40:38,940
that no matter how capable I was,

665
00:40:39,510 --> 00:40:40,610
I still wouldn't surpass you.

666
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:48,570
Enough.

667
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:49,860
You've been busy the whole day.

668
00:40:50,550 --> 00:40:51,260
Go inside your room and sleep.

669
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:53,250
I'll slowly make these noodles.

670
00:40:53,250 --> 00:40:54,530
You can eat them when you wake up.

671
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:55,980
I won't need to wake you up.

672
00:40:56,510 --> 00:40:59,170
The smell of the noodles will do just that.

673
00:41:00,070 --> 00:41:00,530
Go on.

674
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:08,860
Sure.

675
00:41:46,150 --> 00:41:47,170
Mr. Zhao.

676
00:41:48,920 --> 00:41:49,610
My benefactor.

677
00:41:51,760 --> 00:41:53,010
My third enemy.

678
00:41:54,590 --> 00:41:58,010
I used to think my obsession

679
00:41:59,150 --> 00:42:00,900
with vengeance

680
00:42:01,320 --> 00:42:02,780
compelled me to keep investigating

681
00:42:05,760 --> 00:42:08,780
until the truth came out.

682
00:42:12,190 --> 00:42:13,340
Have you thought about what you are going to do?

683
00:42:13,880 --> 00:42:15,340
Should you tell the Emperor directly?

684
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:16,420
No.

685
00:42:17,110 --> 00:42:18,570
I've hidden the bronze fish as well.

686
00:42:19,070 --> 00:42:20,610
We can't go through the Emperor anymore.

687
00:42:22,030 --> 00:42:23,420
We must deal with it ourselves.

688
00:42:30,230 --> 00:42:31,980
Since I've chosen this path,

689
00:42:33,960 --> 00:42:35,650
I have to see through it until the end.

690
00:42:36,670 --> 00:42:37,130
All right.

691
00:42:38,030 --> 00:42:38,980
Move forward

692
00:42:39,630 --> 00:42:42,050
for your past and current self.

693
00:42:44,510 --> 00:42:45,090
Antu.

694
00:42:45,960 --> 00:42:46,820
Make some preparations.

695
00:42:47,480 --> 00:42:49,380
I want to invite Zhao Bingwen to my residence

696
00:42:49,800 --> 00:42:52,420
and confront him.

697
00:43:22,300 --> 00:43:27,020
♪Conceal the ambition in my eyes♪

698
00:43:29,500 --> 00:43:36,140
♪In my palm, I hold a dangerous desire♪

699
00:43:36,700 --> 00:43:39,460
♪Turbulent waves hidden in my sleeves♪

700
00:43:40,060 --> 00:43:42,780
♪Silent thunder echoes around♪

701
00:43:43,060 --> 00:43:45,020
♪However cunning you are♪

702
00:43:45,500 --> 00:43:47,580
♪I can see♪

703
00:43:49,300 --> 00:43:51,420
♪Right through you♪

704
00:43:57,780 --> 00:44:04,820
♪Schemes are my armor♪

705
00:44:04,980 --> 00:44:10,420
♪Overt plans are my weapons♪

706
00:44:11,980 --> 00:44:14,700
♪With restrained fury♪

707
00:44:15,380 --> 00:44:18,060
♪I purge the world's corruption♪

708
00:44:18,260 --> 00:44:20,300
♪The night is not dark♪

709
00:44:20,780 --> 00:44:22,860
♪Because♪

710
00:44:23,980 --> 00:44:29,460
♪My heart burns bright♪

711
00:44:32,260 --> 00:44:35,540
♪I control the shifting clouds♪

712
00:44:35,740 --> 00:44:38,300
♪I command the falling rain♪

713
00:44:38,460 --> 00:44:40,820
♪The compass of the human soul is unpredictable♪

714
00:44:40,940 --> 00:44:45,740
♪There will always be ups and downs♪

715
00:44:46,220 --> 00:44:49,540
♪I hold the power of life and death♪

716
00:44:49,740 --> 00:44:52,300
♪I grant and I take away♪

717
00:44:52,420 --> 00:44:55,980
♪When faith burns like the scorching sun♪

718
00:44:56,020 --> 00:44:59,500
♪I will sing aloud with you♪

719
00:44:59,620 --> 00:45:02,860
♪I am the sowing season♪

720
00:45:02,980 --> 00:45:06,260
♪I am the autumn harvest♪

721
00:45:06,500 --> 00:45:08,660
♪I am the world♪

722
00:45:08,860 --> 00:45:12,420
♪I am the people♪

723
00:45:13,620 --> 00:45:16,700
♪And you are also me♪
